Introduction

Jini, formerly known as Jinni is a South Korean singer, dancer and rapper under ATOC.

On December 9, 2022, JYP Entertainment announced that Jini will be leaving NMIXX due to personal circumstances only 10 months after the groups' debut that year.

She made her solo debut on October 11th, 2023 with the EP, 'An Iron Hand in A Velvet Glove'.
